data.description: Beautiful cottage style craftsman floorplan, open-living design with an expansive living area with large windows and light that look out onto the immense patio and covered porch. The family room is open to the state of the art kitchen and dining room. The chef-style island and eating bar is a perfect gathering in the heart of the home.  Large master suite with sitting area and spacious  closet. Master bath with open/walk-in shower,and  double sinks. The 3rd bedrm/study, or exercise room is off living area.  Located just minutes to shopping, dining, medical facilities and Wrightsville Beach.
